title: BLUS31385-Worms The Revolution Collection
description:
Worms: The Revolution Collection is the definitive gathering of everyone's favourite garden-dwelling grenadiers. This compilation features Worms Revolution, the latest game in the best-selling turn-based series, plus all three content packs, and, as an added bonus Worms 2 Armageddon and all five content packs. Over fifteen years of classic carnage-filled garden warfare, wrapped up in a mystery crate and sealed with a loving poke! 



tested on Habib 4.60
